OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1774019480
OL,3,CDischarging Nottingham attacks killer
OL,4,Cto GP was 'never a good plan'
OL,6,FA doctor has said the decision to
OL,7,Fdischarge a schizophrenic killer to
OL,8,Fhis GP months before he went on a
OL,9,Fviolent rampage was "never a good
OL,10,Fplan", a public inquiry has heard.
OL,12,FValdo Calocane was discharged by
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Healthcare NHS
OL,14,FFoundation Trust in September 2022,
OL,15,Fnine months before the fatal attacks,
OL,16,Fwhich was later criticised in a report
OL,17,Fby the Care Quality Commission.
OL,26,@qD@UOUrD@EO]
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/10
